				<input id="_5" type="checkbox">
				<div class="SIT"><br><ul><li>RhaS activates the rhaBAD and rhaT genes via binding to another inverted-repeat of two sites whose sequence differs from the RhaR consensus binding site .	[<a href="https://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/pubmed/?term=24391637" target="_blank">24391637</a>]<br></li>
